Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE as exclusive selling agents, on behalf of our valued client are pleased to present 14 Fisher St, Silverwater. 

This property boasts a 691sqm* parcel of Industrial land and is ideally located on the Southern side of Fisher St which provides easy access to Silverwater Rd, Parramatta Rd, James Ruse Dr & minutes away to the M4 Motorway. 

14 Fisher St, Silverwater presents a rare opportunity for owner occupiers, investors and developers to acquire a raw development opportunity in the tightly held Silverwater precinct. 

The site presents the opportunity to construct a circa 500sqm* freestanding building (STCA) which makes this property very attractive to owner occupiers and investors.

14 Fisher St, Silverwater benefits from the following key property features:

- 691sqm* site area	
- Fully serviced site
- Square shaped block
- IN1: General Industrial
- Hardstand yard
- Fully secure site
- The property is 18km* west of Sydney CBD
- SOLD as a (Going Concern)! Currently leased for $56,000 Net per annum + GST until 30th of June, 2022

Attention: Builders, owner occupiers, investors & developers!
14 Fisher St, Silverwater will be sold via on-line auction at 3pm, Friday 8th of October.

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.
